<h2>Background</h2>
<p>I co-founded Impact in 2015 and served as a captain until 2019. Our original logo was starting to look stale. The leadership committee agreed it was time for a visual refresh. I had a few ideas and volunteered my time.</p>

<p class="font-medium">My goal was to create a logo that:
    <ul>
        <li>better captured the team identity</li>
        <li>referenced something unique about our culture in Wichita</li>
        <li>would be more adaptable in size, color, and layout</li>
    </ul>
</p>

