<p>I then rearranged the stars into a constellation pattern. That helped the stars feel more natural. Bonus points if you know which constellation I picked. I added a gradient to the debris trail for some visual interest. The state motto was left on the cutting room floor, though it appeared on our jerseys that year!</p>

